name: Enigmatic Planet #2
description:
Second Generated Broadcast from the far reaches of cryptospace. 
Each Enigmatic Planet is unique, much like the planets of our own Universe, procedurally generated from algorithmic code then hand-curated to find the perfect composition to display the elegance of these mysterious worlds. 
Only 10 regions on each planet can be owned by collectors, known as "Barons". As a Baron, you get to govern your own section of land as you see fit, from economy to culture.
